    dc:description "FIGURES 36 – 41. SEM pictures of eggs extracted from a female imago of Sangpradubina thailandica gen. nov. et sp. nov., (36) general outline; (37 – 40) detail of pole; abbreviation: KCT = Knob-coiled Thread; (41) detail of the chorionic structure." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272416/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.272415>
    dc:description "FIGURES 32 – 35. Imago of Sangpradubina thailandica gen. nov. et sp. nov., (32) photograph of male genitalia, ventral view, abbreviation: gp = gonopore; (33) male genitalia, ventral view; (34) male genitalia, lateral view; (35) female last sternites, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/272415/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

